<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= typeof lng !== 'undefined' && lng === 'zh' ? 'zh-CN' : 'en' %>">
<head>
    <!-- Google Tag Manager -->
    <script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src='https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);})(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-K9ZKGLKW');</script>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title><%= typeof title !== 'undefined' ? title : 'Privacy Policy' %></title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Crimson Text', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; 
            color: #334155; 
            background: #f8fafc; 
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 800px; 
            margin: 40px auto; 
            padding: 40px; 
            background: #fff; 
            border-radius: 0; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); 
        }
        h1 { font-size: 28px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 12px; }
        h2 { font-size: 20px; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
        ul { margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .back-link { 
            display: inline-flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            margin-bottom: 24px; 
            color: #aa0000; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-weight: 500; 
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .back-link:hover { color: #880000; text-decoration: underline; }
        .back-link svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; margin-right: 4px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-K9ZKGLKW" height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
            <%= lng === 'zh' ? '返回首页' : 'Back to Home' %>
        </a>

        <% if (typeof lng !== 'undefined' && lng === 'en') { %>
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> April 8, 2026</p>
            
            <p>Hongxiu Custom System ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>When you register or log in, we may collect the following information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Name, email address, and username.</li>
                <li><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> If you choose to log in using third-party services (like Google), we will receive your basic profile information (such as your name, email address, and profile picture) as permitted by you and the third-party service provider.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To create and manage your account.</li>
                <li>To provide, operate, and maintain our customization services.</li>
                <li>To send you administrative information, such as order updates, account notifications, and password reset emails.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Secure Data Handling</h2>
            <p>We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. Your data is stored behind secured networks and is only accessible by a limited number of persons who have special access rights.</p>

            <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
            <p>We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personally identifiable information to outside parties. This does not include reliable third parties who assist us in operating our website or conducting our business, provided that those parties agree to keep this information confidential.</p>

            <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy, you may contact us using the information available on our website.</p>

        <% } else { %>
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p><strong>生效日期：</strong> <%= typeof currentDate !== 'undefined' ? currentDate : '2026年4月8日' %></p>
            
            <p>红绣定制系统（"我们"）非常重视您的隐私。本《Privacy Policy》解释了当您访问我们的网站并使用我们的服务时，我们如何收集、使用、披露和保护您的信息。</p>

            <h2>1. 我们收集的信息</h2>
            <p>当您注册或登录账号时，我们可能会收集以下信息：</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>个人数据：</strong> 姓名、电子邮件地址和用户名。</li>
                <li><strong>第三方身份验证数据：</strong> 如果您选择使用第三方服务（如 Google）登录，我们将接收您授权的第三方平台提供的基本公开信息（如姓名、Email、唯一标识符）。</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. 我们如何使用您的信息</h2>
            <p>我们将收集的信息用于以下目的：</p>
            <ul>
                <li>创建和管理您的系统账号。</li>
                <li>提供、运营和维护我们的定制服务系统。</li>
                <li>向您发送管理通知，如订单状态更新、账号安全提醒以及密码重置邮件。</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. 数据安全保护</h2>
            <p>我们采取各种安全措施来维护您个人信息的安全。您的数据存储在受保护的服务器中，仅允许拥有特殊访问权限的少数人员进行操作。</p>

            <h2>4. 信息共享</h2>
            <p>我们不会向外部平台出售、交易或转让您的个人专有身份信息。这不包括协助我们运营网站、开展业务或为您提供服务的受信任第三方（这些第三方需同意对信息保密）。</p>

            <h2>5. 联系我们</h2>
            <p>如果您对本隐私政策有任何疑问，请通过我们网站上的联系方式与我们取得联系。</p>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
